538
00:34:52.132 --> 00:34:54.009
Whoa. whoa. whoa. whoa! Not another step.

539
00:34:58.138 --> 00:35:00.015
See? Tai chi.

540
00:35:12.402 --> 00:35:14.779
- It's been a while.
- You've done well

541
